#: ../preferences.rst:221
msgid "Please keep in mind that GPU hardware acceleration is experimental at the moment. OpenShot supports both decoding and encoding acceleration. For more information take a look at our `Github HW-ACCEL Doc <https://github.com/OpenShot/libopenshot/blob/develop/doc/HW-ACCEL.md>`_. NOTE: On systems with older graphics cards, hardware acceleration may not always be faster than CPU encoding."
